                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just a small addendum for the Sacrificial pit part.
<br />

<br />
If you are invis and make it past the mobs you can actually jump onto the platform where the corpses are and hug, very tightly, the wall there. Stay in the centre under the robed mobs and you can kill off the nearest 3 corpses to your hearts content.
<br />
If you hit the 4th one (furthest out) then you get aggro and probably need to zone.
<br />

<br />
Once the presence spawns it will be in range and visable (just) for you to do the hand in. Then you get to make another train to the zone as all the traps will have probably reset by then <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
